There&#x27;s a balance between &quot;exploding&quot; offers and hang-around-forever offers. You don&#x27;t want someone to come back 6 months later and say they&#x27;re finally ready to accept your offer.<p>Its not difficult to balance these factors. Just ask, 
&quot;how long do you need to consider this deal?&quot; 
&quot;Two weeks? Four weeks?&quot; 
&quot;If you need more time, just give me a call.&quot;
